        "TileImage": "$($repository cfba4927-82b3-4e66-9816-5888b5c0f2ad).Image",
        "Description": "Dearest 47,\r\rYour first mission as a member of the Yakuza has been issued. Dino Bosco in serious debt to the Yakuza, and after cussing out the men who called to ask for payment in money,  is now going to pay his debts in blood. For good measure, take two of his guards and two movie crew members who are also in debt to the Yakuza. Make the leaders proud, so you can get close to them and end them.\r\rYour Ally,\rL",
